      <h2 class="title text-center">Contact Us</h2>
      <h3>In Person</h3>
      <p>We have regular maker meetups where visitors are welcome. See the <a href="/about#timetable">Timetable</a> for more details of what goes on and check the <a href="#/calendar">Calendar</a> for other times we are open.</p>

      <h3>Committee Members</h3>
      <p>Ballarat Hackerspace is a volunteer based non-profit association, incorporated in Victoria. Our official administrative body is a committee elected by the membership. Our most recent elections were held at the Ballarat Hackerspace AGM on Sat, 9 Jul 2016.</p>
      <p>If you need to contact someone on the committee please use these email links:</p>

