      <h3 id="irc-channel">On IRC</h3>
      <p>Come and hang out on our IRC (Internet Relay Chat) channel on freenode. You can use the web client or your own client at irc.freenode.net #bhack.</p>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=bhack">Direct Webchat Link</a></li>
        <li><a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/bhack">Direct link for IRC clients</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Google+</h3>
      <p>A lot of discussion and announcements happen on our <a href="http://plus.bhack.in/">Google+ community page</a>, both members and non-members are welcome.</p>

      <h3>Twitter</h3>
      <p>You can tweet to <a href="https://twitter.com/bhackerspace">@bhackerspace</a>. Follow the account to get announcements and news from the Ballarat Hackerspace.</p>

      <h3>Telegram</h3>
      <p>You can join our Telegram channel at <a href="https://telegram.me/ballarathackerspace">telegram.me/ballarathackerspace</a></p>
